852
00:55:25,531 --> 00:55:27,701
A business proposition

853
00:55:27,992 --> 00:55:30,542
from our American friend,

854
00:55:31,037 --> 00:55:32,407
Henri Dussard.

855
00:55:34,415 --> 00:55:36,245
His four chimpanzees,

856
00:55:36,917 --> 00:55:41,087
