858
00:55:44,592 --> 00:55:48,012
Are at the disposal, free of charge,

859
00:55:48,554 --> 00:55:51,814
of all who want their crops harvested.

860
00:55:54,143 --> 00:55:57,103
The olives will be purchased

861
