866
00:56:12,453 --> 00:56:14,713
This is a trick! It's impossible.

867
00:56:14,997 --> 00:56:18,167
Oh, if <i>Monsieur</i> Dussard
says it can be done...

868
00:56:18,459 --> 00:56:20,089
Then I believe him.

869
