Relax.

891
00:57:37,621 --> 00:57:39,461
Uh, everything's going to be okay.

892
00:57:39,582 --> 00:57:41,542
<i>Merci, monsieur. Merci.</i>

893
00:57:41,625 --> 00:57:42,955
