<i>monsieur.</i>

897
00:57:52,845 --> 00:57:53,845
Mmm?

898
00:57:54,472 --> 00:57:56,722
Offering your monkeys to pick olives.

899
00:57:56,891 --> 00:57:59,311
Oh. Oh, yeah! That.

900
00:57:59,393 --> 00:58:01,563
