960
01:01:46,787 --> 01:01:48,367
Oh,

961
01:01:48,622 --> 01:01:49,622
that.

962
01:01:50,874 --> 01:01:51,964
You do not like me?

963
01:01:52,835 --> 01:01:53,915
That's my trouble, Maria.

964
01:01:54,461 --> 01:01:55,461
I like you too much.

965
01:01:56,630 --> 01:01:58,340
Hank, <i>cheri!</i>

966
01:01:59,174 --> 01:02:00,304
